[12.85361, "o", "\u001b[90m│\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m◆\u001b[39m  How to handle existing files?\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m●\u001b[39m Overwrite all\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m○\u001b[22m \u001b[2mSkip (keep existing)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m○\u001b[22m \u001b[2mAsk for each file\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m└\u001b[39m\r\n"]
